These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, tiparillo, cain, swisher
1. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
3. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Cigar   | cain | tiparillo | bluemaster | swisher |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, sports, comedy, fantasy
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching crime movies is on the far left##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | comedy | sports | fantasy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, sunflower, tulip, lily
1. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
2. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growslily##1
3. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Flower   | tulip | daisy | sunflower | lily |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
