1. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
3. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Music-Genre   | indie | classical | folk | r&b |

