2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |   3    |     4     |
| Transport   | roller | jet-ski | ship | bike |

